1.title: Nonexisting category
1.description: The Category Object is in doesn't exist or there is a typo in Category name in category data or the associated folder name

2.title: Nonexisting main version
2.description: The Main version Object has doesn't exist or there is a typo in Main version name in category data  or the associated folder name

3.title: Nonexisting source object
3.description: The Source object Object refers to doesn't exist or there is a typo in Source object name in category data file or the associated filename

4.title: An error occured during gsm compilation
4.description: LP_XMLConverter.exe printed out some kind of error

5.title: 0 indexing in array, NOT done
5.description: Call and/or associated database entry wants to write an array[0] while GDL arrays' indexing starts from 1

6.title: Nonexisting translator
6.description: Call contains a parameter that cannot be translated into an ARCHICAD parameter or there is a typo in translation file

7.title: Malformed request
7.description: At least one required field is missing from request

8.title: Bad parameter type
8.description: A parameter is given a bad data, like string instead of int.
